obj_root_law:
  slug the-intelligence-organisations-restriction-of-rights-act-1985
  handle (1811)
  collectionHandle 123456789/1362
  title `The Intelligence Organisations (Restriction of Rights) Act, 1985`
  actNumber (58)
  enactmentDate 1985-09-06
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/1811`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  actYear (1985)
  ministry `Ministry of Home Affairs`
  department `Department of Internal Security`
  longTitle `An Act to provide for the restriction of certain rights conferred by Part III of the Constitution in their application to the members of certain organisations established by the Central Government for purposes of intelligence or counter-intelligence so as to ensure the proper discharge of their duties and the maintenance of discipline among them.`
  enforcementDate 09-11-1985
  notification `9th December, 1985, vide notification No. S.O. 885(E), dated 9th December, 1985, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3(ii).`
